               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290611-307-cd1619" type="crimeDate">28th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-307-off1618 t18290611-307-cd1619"></join>, 1 bell, value 4s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t18290611-307-victim2211" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Voyce
                  <interp inst="t18290611-307-victim2211" type="surname" value="Voyce"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290611-307-victim2211" type="given" value="John"></interp>
